node.text: Hey everyone! Welcome to my IGTV! Today i'm giving you my everyday makeup routine for when I'm working from home. Whether thats zoom meetings, home shoots, Insta work or even tik toks haha ;) Obviously 50% of quarantine i've been completely bare faced and letting my skin rest:) but thought it'd be nice to share this with you all! I'd love to see you guys recreate this look at home and tag me in it!! xx Jas
